              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The outgoing reaction residues were",
                "distinguished based on their energy loss determined",
                "in the S800 ionization chamber and the time of flight",
                "measured between the object position of the analysis",
                "beam line and the plastic scintillator at the back of",
                "the S800 focal plane."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The inclusive two-neutron removal cross section for",
                "the formation of 36Ca was determined from the",
                "efficiency corrected number of 36Ca residues detected",
                "in the S800 focal plane, the number of incident 38Ca",
                "projectiles, and the areal density of the target."
              ]
            }
